Ore in the mines can be freely collected and will be restored when the map is moved.
You can also save the game when you move to each level.
However, once you enter the mine
You won't be able to change jobs until you come back.
You can't warp or otherwise come back.
The damage floor after the dry tier is for lightly-armored jobs.
It is not recommended, as you will take a lot of damage!
